media:group.media:description:
Level 1: You're pretty safe in this part of the gym. The girls are pretty civil and approachable. Feel free to treat them like any other girl. 

Level 2: Whoa, whoa, whoa, careful there bud. This part of the gym is for members only. You gotta be able to bench at least 169 before you should think about asking for her number. Hell, I'm pretty sure most of them would be dangerous if they didn't know human speech. But hey, you wanna dip your toes into that pool I ain't gonna stop you.
